Perhaps because there was a funeral,
the atmosphere has become somewhat
sad, and I'm feeling down, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300071_02msg0002

I came to pray for my family's
health, but... I have to go and
pray quietly for this one, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300071_02msg0003

As you can see, my daughter
won't be quiet, so I can't
go right now... mo.
